      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented QA procedures and regression test suite sufficient for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent v2022R2 is used with documented version control, regression testing, and user qualification records. QA procedures align with ASME V&V 10 guidance. Required level 2 is met."
