      "rationale": "Experimental conditions are drawn from the FDA generic blood pump dataset with documented fluid properties (bovine blood analogue at 37°C), rotational speeds (2000–3500 RPM), and flow rates (2.5–7.5 L/min). Traceability to published FDA protocol is confirmed."
    },
