      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) within 25% of experimental values across the 5 operating points; pressure head within 10%.",
      "rationale": "NIH predictions agree with experimental data within 18% across all five operating points. Pressure-head predictions are within 7%. Output comparison criteria are met at the required level."
